# COMPLETE DIGITAL ASSET JOURNEY STRUCTURE

```
1. Intro              → Define & reassure
2. Platform selection → Speed & momentum  
3. Instruction setup  → Clarity & security
4. Review             → Confidence checkpoint
5. Success            → Closure & control
6. Dashboard          → Integration
```

