# UI COMPONENT PATTERNS

## Headlines
```
❌ "Let's list your digital assets"
✅ "Organise your digital accounts"

❌ "Why add assets?"
✅ "Why this matters"

❌ "Instructions after death"
✅ "Instruction upon activation"
```

## Security Reassurance Block
```
🛡️ We do not store passwords or login credentials.
This information will only be accessible according to your estate instructions.
```

## CTA Hierarchy
```
Primary: Action-oriented, specific
  ✅ "Add digital asset"
  ✅ "Save asset"
  ✅ "Return to dashboard"
  
Secondary: Subtle, non-competing
  ✅ "Back"
  ✅ "Add another digital asset"
  
Avoid:
  ❌ "Confirm"
  ❌ "Submit"
  ❌ "Finalise"
```

## Platform-Specific Smart Defaults
```dart
switch (platformCategory) {
  case 'social': return 'Memorialise account';
  case 'subscription': return 'Close subscription';
  case 'finance': return 'Transfer access to executor';
  case 'crypto': return 'Transfer access to executor';
}
```

